Creating memorable and magical experiences at the UK’s biggest and best attractions, a Merlin Gift Card is your ultimate passport to unlock EPIC togetherness at over 30 of the UK’s most beloved attractions! From aquariums to theme parks, dungeons to historic buildings, there are countless experiences to enjoy across the UK. Merlin Entertainments has dedicated itself to crafting magical memories, hosting over 60 million visitors every year.
From the magical worlds of LEGOLAND Windsor Resort and Alton Towers Resort to the fascinating depths of SEA LIFE aquariums and the immersive fun at Madame Tussauds, the Merlin Gift Card opens the door to endless possibilities. Valid at all Merlin's UK attractions, it allows you to purchase entry tickets, hotel stays, and more.